# ─── Sync script ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by `npm run sync:sources` to authenticate against the GitHub API.
# A fine-grained PAT with read-only access to public repos in the farcasterorg
# org is sufficient. Falls back to unauthenticated requests (lower rate limit).
GITHUB_TOKEN=
# GH_TOKEN is accepted as an alias (e.g. when using the gh CLI default).
# GH_TOKEN=

# ─── SNAP market dashboard ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional override for the Dexscreener pairs API URL used by the /api/snap-market
# route. Defaults to the canonical SNAP/ETH pair on Ethereum mainnet.
# Only change this if the pair migrates or you need to point at a test endpoint.
DEXSCREENER_PAIR_URL=https://api.dexscreener.com/latest/dex/pairs/ethereum/0x72a70a747a8390caf1aad3fb1de3564b55871f137539e498d30f02b1167742ea
